    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁 Alex Gerko 的 XTX 将斥资 10 亿欧元打造机器学习数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/gerko-s-xtx-to-build-1-billion-data-hub-in-machine-learning-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁亚历克斯·格科（Alex Gerko）的量化交易公司 XTX Markets 正在投资超过 10 亿欧元（10 亿美元）在芬兰建立五个数据中心，以支持其日益增长的机器学习应用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/gerko-s-xtx-to-build-1-billion-data-hub-in-machine-learning-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼部长称苹果即将解除对 iPhone 的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/apple-close-to-deal-to-lift-indonesian-iphone-ban-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位政府部长透露，印度尼西亚即将与苹果公司就一项投资计划达成协议，该计划将解除该国对 iPhone 16 的销售禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/apple-close-to-deal-to-lift-indonesian-iphone-ban-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 04:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典垃圾邮件拦截器 Truecaller 挑战人工智能语音克隆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/spam-blocker-truecaller-aims-to-counter-ai-voice-scam-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典的 Truecaller AB 是一家来电显示和垃圾电话拦截应用程序的开发商，该公司正在部署技术，以打击越来越多使用人工智能生成的语音克隆来欺诈电话用户的犯罪分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/spam-blocker-truecaller-aims-to-counter-ai-voice-scam-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更便宜的电动汽车将考验印度人对耗油汽车的热爱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/cheaper-electric-cars-will-test-india-s-love-of-gas-guzzlers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当 Anant Vijay Kala 的旧车达到新德里严格的 15 年使用年限时，他在一个较小的城市将其出售，并用这笔钱部分资助他的下一辆汽车 — — 一辆汽油驱动的斯柯达 Kushaq。他从未考虑过更清洁的替代品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/cheaper-electric-cars-will-test-india-s-love-of-gas-guzzlers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普交易压力下，SK 海力士今年上涨 26%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/sk-hynix-s-26-gain-this-year-under-pressure-from-trump-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，韩国 SK 海力士股价在人工智能的推动下上涨了 26%，但这一涨势却面临威胁，因为政治问题和估值促使本地投资者转向专注于国内市场的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/sk-hynix-s-26-gain-this-year-under-pressure-from-trump-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孙正义的 AI 愿景实现后，软银股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/softbank-shares-soar-on-100-billion-ai-push-with-openai-oracle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团宣布将与 OpenAI、甲骨文公司和阿布扎比支持的 MGX 合作开展一项 5000 亿美元的项目，为 ChatGPT 创建者在美国建设数据中心和基础设施。此后，该公司股价上涨 12%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/softbank-shares-soar-on-100-billion-ai-push-with-openai-oracle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称他愿意接受埃隆·马斯克或拉里·埃里森收购 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-open-to-musk-or-ellison-purchasing-tiktok</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他愿意让亿万富翁支持者埃隆·马斯克或甲骨文公司董事长拉里·埃里森与美国政府成立合资企业，收购社交视频应用 TikTok。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-open-to-musk-or-ellison-purchasing-tiktok</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 23:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
